title: AB Soul Interview
itunes:title: AB Soul Interview
description:
AB- Soul stopped by the Breakfast Club to promote his new album "DWTW," talks about his beef with Jay Electronica and gives confirmation on a Kendrick Lamar and J. Cole collaboration. A disrespectful airport rant earns Young Thug Donkey of the Day honors.
